      <title>消息人士称，日本央行认为没有必要在 12 月结束负利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/boj-is-said-to-see-little-need-to-end-negative-rate-in-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，日本央行官员认为本月没有必要急于废除全球最后一次负利率，因为他们尚未看到足够的证据表明工资增长将支持可持续通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/boj-is-said-to-see-little-need-to-end-negative-rate-in-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 07:40:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
